displayName: LessonStream: Comparing Exponential Functions
description: In this video, students will explore exponential growth and decay functions with Mr. Tarver.
keywords: ["Using Exponential Equations","Investigating Growth and Decay"]

displayName: LessonStream: Expanding and Factoring Linear Expressions
curriculumTreeDisplayName: LessonStream: Expanding and Factoring Linear Expressions
description: In this video, students will factor and expand linear expressions using the Distributive Property with Mr. Hua.
keywords: ["Multiple Representations of Equations and Inequalities","Reasoning Algebraically"]

displayName: LessonStream: Solving Multiplication Equations Using a Double Number Line
curriculumTreeDisplayName: LessonStream: Solving Multiplication Equations Using a Double Number Line
description: In this video, students will use a double number line to represent and solve multiplication equations with Mrs. Kelly!
keywords: ["Equations","Determining Unknown Quantities"]

displayName: LessonStream: Analyzing and Using Data to Make Predictions with Exponential Functions
curriculumTreeDisplayName: LessonStream: Analyzing and Using Data to Make Predictions with Exponential Functions
description: In this video, students will determine an appropriate regression equation to represent a real-world situation and make predictions using the equation with Ms. Reddig.
keywords: ["Using Exponential Equations","Investigating Growth and Decay"]

displayName: SkillStream: Solving Exponential Equations by Graphing
curriculumTreeDisplayName: SkillStream: Solving Exponential Equations by Graphing
description: In this video, students will explore using graphs to solve exponential equations that represent real-world situations with Mr. Ahdoot.
keywords: ["Exponential Expressions and Equations","Targeted Instruction for Investigating Growth and Decay"]

displayName: SkillStream: Writing and Using Linear Models of Bivariate Data
curriculumTreeDisplayName: SkillStream: Writing and Using Linear Models of Bivariate Data
description: In this video, students will write the equation of a linear model of bivariate data and use the equation to solve problems and make predictions with Mr. Ahdoot.
keywords: ["Scatter Plots and Linear Models","Targeted Instruction for Developing Function Foundations"]

displayName: LessonStream: Determining the Best Fit to Model Data
curriculumTreeDisplayName: LessonStream: Determining the Best Fit to Model Data
description: In this video, students will explore exponential regression equations that model real-world situations with Ms. Reddig.
keywords: ["Using Exponential Equations","Investigating Growth and Decay"]

displayName: SkillStream: Defining Independent and Dependent Variables
curriculumTreeDisplayName: SkillStream: Defining Independent and Dependent Variables
